abstract: Shaun Donovan, a former cabinet secretary, files paperwork to run for mayor.
snippet: Shaun Donovan, a former cabinet secretary, files paperwork to run for mayor.
lead_paragraph: Shaun Donovan, a former housing secretary and budget director under President Barack Obama, filed paperwork on Monday to run for mayor of New York City.
